{"about_the_game":"At first glance looks like a typical day in the office, but now your responsibilities are completely different. Pick up furniture, throw and smash it. Destroy walls, floor and celling. Get rid of the third floor or demolish the building to the base. Make employees dance, run or throw furniture - this will help to make a fuss. Explore the office building and find the way to destroy it in a new way. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140880/extras/General1.gif?t=1724993955\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MAIN FEATURES:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Become an empathetic colleague</u></h2>You see an employee hard working at his workplace? Crash his chair and table, so he can rest up for a little while.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140880/extras/HelpCollegue.gif?t=1724993955\" /><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Make open space more open</u></h2>Destroy the large three-floor office to the base. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140880/extras/Destroy2.gif?t=1724993955\" /><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Make something really crazy</u></h2>Play in various odd game modes such as Total Diarrhea, Froggy, etc.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140880/extras/Froggy.gif?t=1724993955\" /><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Relax and have fun</u></h2>If you are tired of carrying and throwing objects, you can make your colleagues dance or run to help you cope with the correction of office architecture.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140880/extras/MakeAFuss3.gif?t=1724993955\" /></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140880/page_b